"Our Heritage" or team photo — Neither page currently has a photo of Amir, the family, the warehouse, or the Sparkbrook location. This is a massive missed opportunity. The research doc talks about 60+ years of family heritage being a key differentiator — but there's no visual proof anywhere. I'd add a small heritage strip between the benefits and product sections on the food service page: a photo of the warehouse, a photo of Amir, and a photo of the original Ladypool Road shop (if one exists).
